title: New Seasonal Routes from Rhodes by Aegean Airlines
text:
New Seasonal Routes from Rhodes by Aegean Airlines   
Sep 23, 2015 eTN   
Next summer, in 2016, Aegean Airlines plans to introduce 2 brand new summer seasonal routes. One of them is from Rhodes, including the launch of Marseille and the other one is Milan Malpensa. Planned schedule as follow. 
eff 12APR16 Rhodes – Marseille 1 weekly A3422 RHO0715 – 0910MRS 320 2 A3423 MRS0955 – 1350RHO 320 2 
eff 27JUN16 Rhodes – Milan Malpensa 2 weekly until 07SEP16 A3492 RHO0730 – 0915MXP 320 3 A3492 RHO0750 – 0935MXP 320 1 
A3493 MXP1000 – 1340RHO 320 3 A3493 MXP1020 – 1400RHO 320 1
